    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summoners War: Chronicles is a summoning RPG that explores the conflicts and choices that shaped the world found in the original Summoners War: Sky Arena.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose one of six Summoners—Orbia, Kina, Cleaf, Soleta, Heath, or Jin—to explore vast continents, summon Monsters, and battle against the darkness seeping through the Rift of Worlds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/16e21dedc4cf42076a3a9686e5a26d62.avif?t=1767837828\" width=614 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>KEY GAME FEATURES</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose Your Character</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Each Summoner has a unique role and skill set. Choose the one that suits your playstyle and embark on your journey!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/353c06d41bac76df35cdd527c6f21e31.poster.avif?t=1767837828\" width=614 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/353c06d41bac76df35cdd527c6f21e31.webm?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/353c06d41bac76df35cdd527c6f21e31.mp4?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight Alongside Your Monsters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Summon a team from over 550 Monsters and join them on the battlefield for the first time! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/debe2273ca4065627d20a2e9abb39097.poster.avif?t=1767837828\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/debe2273ca4065627d20a2e9abb39097.webm?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/debe2273ca4065627d20a2e9abb39097.mp4?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Action RPG Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evade enemy attacks, command your Monsters, and cast spells in real-time combat encounters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/ab9bdbe26a9c33747544bb06596275bc.poster.avif?t=1767837828\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/ab9bdbe26a9c33747544bb06596275bc.webm?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/ab9bdbe26a9c33747544bb06596275bc.mp4?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Endless Adventure</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a vast world comprised of multiple continents.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/f9735df66fba18720b05c2103003f696.poster.avif?t=1767837828\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/f9735df66fba18720b05c2103003f696.webm?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/f9735df66fba18720b05c2103003f696.mp4?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Modes</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into loot-filled Dungeons, climb the many-floored Ascensions, and take on Raids with friends! Then head to the Arena to compete against other players!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/9bd8a820d4c122d8563422cba4fc4ef2.poster.avif?t=1767837828\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/9bd8a820d4c122d8563422cba4fc4ef2.webm?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/9bd8a820d4c122d8563422cba4fc4ef2.mp4?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Summoners War Reimagined</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the expanded universe of Summoners War, and immerse yourself in the untold story of the Rahil Kingdom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/cbf198ce94eee739cf40e685e349304d.poster.avif?t=1767837828\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/cbf198ce94eee739cf40e685e349304d.webm?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2167580/extras/cbf198ce94eee739cf40e685e349304d.mp4?t=1767837828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
